articles.author: Ryan Grim, Jeremy Scahill
articles.title: Medical Workers Evacuated From Gaza, but 3 Americans Refuse to Leave - The Intercept
articles.description: Remaining health care workers won’t leave European Hospital in Khan Younis until Israel stops blocking entry of new medical personnel.
articles.content: Some 20 American and British medical workers who had been unable to leave Gaza were evacuated from the European Hospital in Khan Younis on Friday, though three American members of medical missions re… [+5901 chars]
